               stealing, on the <rs id="t18340904-65-cd363" type="crimeDate">22nd of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340904-65-off362 t18340904-65-cd363"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 2s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18340904-65-victim446" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Drew
                     <interp inst="t18340904-65-victim446" type="surname" value="Drew"></interp>
